        <p>PixTech is a publicly owned company (NASDAQ
        &quot;PIXT&quot;) which manufactures field emission
        displays (FEDs), flat panels which provide the picture
        quality of a television tube (CRT) with the slender
        packaging of a liquid crystal display (LCD). PixTech also
        licenses its technology. The company's displays are
        bought by test, measurement and medical instrument
        manufacturers and cockpit display integrators who require
        higher image brightness, wider viewing angles, lower
        power consumption and video-speed operation in greater
        temperature extremes than available with other displays. </p>
        <p>&#160; </p>
